This category contains specific pages for various [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|Worlds]]. It is not a comprehensive list.

World pages should only be created for the following types of worlds:
* Official VRChat worlds
* Worlds featured by VRChat (Spotlight and special event categories such as VKet and Jams)
* Worlds that meet all of the following notability criteria:
** Worlds that have made it out of [[Special:MyLanguage/Community_Labs|Community Labs]]
** Worlds with at least 10,000 visits or 1,000 favorites

Pages should include the filled out [[Special:MyLanguage/Template:Infobox/World/doc|world template infobox]], and contain some degree of additional information describing the world.

Worlds that were made by the Community (anyone other than VRChat itself) belong in the <code>Community:</code> namespace. Please add <code>Community:</code> in front of the page name for these. To learn more about namespaces, also see [[VRCWiki:How_to_Contribute#Namespaces]] .